[[# speech]]
++ speech

How to make the computer talk.

**posix shell:**

On Mac OSX the command {{say}} can also be executed from the bash or zsh prompt:

[[code]]
say "I'm a Mac"
[[/code]]

On Ubuntu Linux this command can be used:

[[code]]
espeak "I'm Unix"
[[/code]]

